Had one heck of a YEE YEE time mudding my 2wd truck 🤘

Really got my adrenaline pumping several times, when I had to drive through deep water and almost got stuck in muddy trenches on inclines...at one point my entire front end got air from sending it up the water-filled holes 😂
.
Really wish I had filmed it all, would’ve been pretty epic video, but I was focused on getting out of there WITH my truck 😂
.
Def a day I will never forget 🤙
